txt.en: Defeat spirits in the Dead Marshes ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
Some disturbance has wakened many of the dead within the marshes. These spirits will work no good in the world while they prowl.\n\nYou should defeat a number of fell spirits in the Dead Marshes.
Some disturbance has wakened many of the dead spirits within the marshes. They should really be returned to rest.\n\nDefeat a good number of fell spirits in the Dead Marshes.
